t <br />\n我以前就係好似你個現任咁<br />\n自此我完全唔再信任何人<br />\n你啲咁自私嘅人渣邊個同你一齊都係不幸"},{"pid":"73648a366bacac377afa8b8273bdf6de76ace9d0","tid":1665370,"uid":102575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"樓主好好反省自己然後兩邊都斬䌫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa7df42aab8cd1415d31c80399fe34a3ca66fdd","tid":1665370,"uid":153016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"你放手啦 現任值得擁有更好"},{"pid":"a5b5578e9314528a7c91e6d9564e7d19f834f67f","tid":1665370,"uid":170176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"如果中意左同事就放過男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你咁介意同事嘅眼光嘅話<br />\n其實你都唔係好中意你個同事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你中意佢你唔會去諗咁多野啦"}]}